OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fovernight. Largely clear at first, but
OL,7,Fcloud will tend to thicken in places
OL,8,Fbringing cloudier conditions for some
OL,9,Fby dawn. Winds generally easing across
OL,10,Fthe region and turning chilly, with a
OL,11,Ffrost possible in sheltered rural
OL,12,Fspots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FCloudy start in places, but
OL,15,Fwidespread sunshine developing through
OL,16,Fthe morning to give a generally fine
OL,17,Fday. Feeling cooler however,
OL,18,Fparticularly towards the northeast
OL,19,Fcoast, with a fresh easterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
